{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"在时代的前列——欢呼北京市革命委员会诞生","authors":["郑军华"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":4,"day":22}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在时代的前列"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——欢呼北京市革命委员会诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑军华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗漫卷迎东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢声如雷震长空；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，敲起进军的鼓点阔步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级革命派志壮心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一张马列主义的大字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把全世界轰动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它冲开了重重迷雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使全国革命烈火顿时熊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看雪片般的传单、大字报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过黄河、长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到遥远的西藏、新疆、海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喧闹的城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"僻静的乡村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里没有这革命的火种！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方的地平线上红光万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民个个是英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵放开雄浑的嗓门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向旧世界发出挑战的怒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横扫一切害人虫！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹响了时代的进军号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在文化革命的最前列猛打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛冲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁般的队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结成一道红色长虹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响彻三山的战斗口号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象雷声震动太空；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举起心爱的《毛主席语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"录》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把环球照得通红通红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看工人农民的队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以排山倒海之势，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向走资本主义道路的当权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派进攻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让一切牛鬼蛇神暴露在光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天化日之下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把旧市委的修正主义集团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一扫而空！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们向全世界发出胜利的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京市革命委员会在斗争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中诞生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少双眼睛日夜注视着北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人的脉搏和北京一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界革命的战友将同声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义中国蒸蒸日上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义、修正主义日暮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"途穷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，看崭新的北京吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的革命小将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上飞泛着胜利的笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"容；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“抓革命，促生产”的伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢记在工农革命群众的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的老干部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀出来了，跟上去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命立新劳建新功！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都有一个共同的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让历史的巨轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远绕着毛泽东思想的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轴心转动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看海洋般的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北京上空飞舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽情歌唱啊，尽情高呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请毛主席检阅我们大会师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的队伍！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动手中的“语录”吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用惊天动地的吼声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向全世界宣布："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要更高地举起毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想伟大红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要绘出新北京的蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取得夺权斗争的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是万里长征的第一步！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发扬革命的闯劲吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂动乘胜追击的战鼓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个欣欣向荣的人民革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍然屹立在祖国的首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}